# plan/facts/18-production-compound-agent-evidence.bn
#
# Production-deployed compound-AI-systems evidence (fetched 2026-05-03)
# that lifts cheapcode's substrate-pattern from research-only mutawatir
# (facts/14) to research-PLUS-production. This is the strongest
# transfer-illah we can compose: the same architectural pattern
# (orchestrator + multi-witness + synthesizer) is empirically deployed
# at production scale by frontier labs and shows quantified lift.

# ============================================================
# E1: Anthropic multi-agent research system (Anthropic 2025-06)
# ============================================================
# Orchestrator-worker pattern: Claude Opus 4 lead + Claude Sonnet 4
# subagents in parallel → outperforms single-agent Claude Opus 4 by
# 90.2% on internal research eval. Token cost: ~15× chat (or ~4×
# subagent-vs-chat). Real-world impact documented: users save days
# of work, find overlooked opportunities, navigate complex healthcare
# decisions. THIS IS DIRECT PRODUCTION VALIDATION OF cheapcode's
# substrate pattern.
lemma anthropic_orchestrator_subagent_lifts_research_eval_90_2pct_at_15x_token_cost_l3_production
  proves True
  by audit anthropic-multi-agent-research-system-fetched-2026-05-03

# ============================================================
# E2: Berkeley/BAIR Compound AI Systems thesis (Zaharia et al. 2024-02)
# ============================================================
# 4-reason argument: (1) better cost/perf — scaling 30→35% via model
# is inefficient vs engineering 80% via sampling+testing; (2) dynamic
# knowledge via retrieval; (3) enhanced control / verification; (4)
# perf flexibility. Canonical examples (production-deployed):
#   - AlphaCode 2: ~1M solutions sampled+filtered → 85th percentile
#   - AlphaGeometry: LLM + symbolic solver → olympiad geometry
#   - Medprompt: NN-search + CoT + ensemble vote → beats medical-finetune
#   - Gemini CoT@32: 32 chained calls + agreement selection
# THESIS: SOTA is increasingly compound, not monolithic. Direct
# substrate-pattern validation at L3 from senior infra-systems lab.
lemma bair_compound_ai_systems_thesis_4_reasons_4_canonical_production_examples_l3_2024
  proves True
  by audit bair-blog-2024-02-18-compound-ai-systems-fetched-2026-05-03

# ============================================================
# Composed — production + research convergence
# ============================================================
# Anthropic production (E1) + Berkeley thesis (E2) + facts/14 academic
# mutawatir (9+ groups) + facts/05 prior production evidence (Devin,
# Claude Code, NVIDIA NeMo) = >12 independent witnesses across academic
# and production strata. The substrate pattern is over-determined;
# transfer to cheapcode-witness v1x rides at maximum L3 ceiling 0.85.
lemma compound_agent_pattern_over_determined_via_research_plus_production_witnesses_2026_05_03
  proves True
  by audit anthropic-bair-facts-14-facts-05-aggregation-2026-05-03
